🌍 ReGenesis — Step-by-Step Working

1️⃣ Power ON

The ESP32 starts the whole system and initializes:

DHT22 sensor

OLED display

LED

buzzer



---

2️⃣ Temperature & Humidity Detection

The DHT22 sensor continuously reads:

temperature

humidity


from the environment.


---

3️⃣ Data Processing

ESP32 receives the sensor data and processes it in real time.


---

4️⃣ OLED Display Output

The OLED screen displays:

project name

current temperature

humidity level

system status


Example:

Temp: 36°C
Humidity: 62%
ALERT!


---

5️⃣ Safety Check

The system compares the temperature with the safety threshold.

If:

Temperature > 35°C

then it detects danger.


---

6️⃣ Alert Activation

When danger is detected:

red LED blinks

buzzer alarm turns ON

OLED shows “ALERT!”



---

7️⃣ Safe Condition

If temperature becomes normal:

LED turns OFF

buzzer stops

OLED shows “SAFE”
8️⃣ Continuous Monitoring
The process repeats every few seconds for real-time disaster/environment monitoring.
🚨 Purpose of Project
ReGenesis helps in:
disaster monitoring
heat/fire alert systems
industrial safety
emergency environmental monitoring
smart rescue systems
